    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Glans and foreskin may be swollen, erythematous, tender, or itchy\nSevere cases may involve difficulty voiding, foul smell, and penile discharge/purulence\nErythematous papular\nrash\nwith satellite lesions = fungal",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
